videos.description: Rico Dowdle runs 1 yd for a TD to take a 7-0 lead
videos.headline: Gamecocks jump out to early lead

videos.description: Defensive back Chris Lammons is ejected from the game against Tennessee after throwing several punches on a play in the endzone.
videos.headline: South Carolina DB ejected from game for throwing punches

videos.description: Jalen Hurd runs for 1 yd TD
videos.headline: Tennessee ties it up after short TD run

videos.description: Joshua Dobbs pass intercepted by Jamarcus King at the Tennessee 31 yard line
videos.headline: Interception sets up Gamecocks with great field position

videos.description: Jake Bentley pass complete to Bryan Edwards for 17 yds and a TD to take 14-7 lead
videos.headline: South Carolina takes advantage of turnover with TD pass

videos.description: Evan Berry gets the kick off at his own goal line and then goes 100 yards the other way untouched to pull Tennessee back to 17-14.
videos.headline: Zero to 100 in a flash for Tennessee kick off return TD

videos.description: Joshua Dobbs fumbles and the ball is recovered by Darius English at the 50 yard line
videos.headline: 4th quarter fumble kills Tennessee drive

videos.description: USC goes up 24-14 as Jake Bentley completes 35 yd TD to K.C. Crosby
videos.headline: Long TD pass extends Gamecock lead

videos.description: Vols cut lead to 24-21 as Joshua Dobbs completes 6 yd TD pass to Jauan Jennings
videos.headline: Tennessee responds with TD reception

videos.description: Aaron Medley 58 yd FG missed and South Carolina wins 24-21
videos.headline: Vols 58 yard FG attempt comes up short as time expires
